title: Devo - Hardcore (Fan Remaster)[FLAC]
description:
For all the Spuds ! A lot of time and energy went into this remaster, I'm very proud of it. I hope all the Devo fans will love this. 

Notes

*This is not the 2014 reissue, it's copied from the 1990.
*It's not a geniue FLAC format, I remastered from MP3 files (still sounds good)
*I put all the best tracks together and the worst tracks together (personally opinion)
*I worked hard on "Stop look and listen" but I had a difficult time getting the Lead vocal properly balanced. 

Please leave feedback and comments. And enjoy spuds - Kasper
